olm MacLeod 3rd Clan Chief78歲，母親Lady Martha Domhnall - Lady of Mar49歲。她於大約1395年與Murdoch Mackenzie 5th Laird of Kintail在蘇格蘭洛-爾金泰爾結婚。他們至少是1個兒子的父母。她去世於1416年在蘇格蘭享年42歲，埋葬在蘇格蘭。"},"zh-hans":{"1374–1416":"1374年–1416年","1370–Male":"1370年–殁","1363–1416":"1363年–1416年","1398–1488":"1398年–1488年","1296–1380":"1296年–1380年","1325–1402":"1325年–1402年","before 1368":"1368年之前","5 September 1402":"1402年9月5日","1374":"1374年","1363":"1363年","1296":"1296年","1370":"1370年","1380":"1380年","1402":"1402年","1325":"1325年","1488":"1488年","1398":"1398年","about 1395":"大约1395年","1416":"1416年","Scotland":"苏格兰","Stornoway Castle, Lewis, Scotland":"苏格兰洛-爾斯托諾維艾","Ross-shire, Scotland":"苏格兰洛-爾","Lochbroom, Ross-shire, Scotland":"苏格兰洛-爾洛賀布盧姆","Kintail, Ross-shire, Scotland":"苏格兰洛-爾金泰爾","lifeSummary":"当Finguala MacLeod of Harris于1374年出生在苏格兰洛-爾时，她的父亲Malcolm MacLeod 3rd Clan Chief78岁，母亲Lady Martha Domhnall - Lady of Mar49岁。她于大约1395年与Murdoch Mackenzie 5th Laird of Kintail在苏格兰洛-爾金泰爾结婚。他们至少是1个儿子的父母。她去世于1416年在苏格兰享年42岁，埋葬在苏格兰。"},"hr":{"1374–1416":"1374.–1416.","1370–Male":"1370–preminuo","1363–1416":"1363–1416.","1398–1488":"1398.–1488","1296–1380":"1296–1380.","1325–1402":"1325–1402","before 1368":"prije 1368.","5 September 1402":"5. rujna 1402.","1374":"1374.","1363":"1363","1296":"1296","1370":"1370","1380":"1380.","1402":"1402","1325":"1325","1488":"1488","1398":"1398.","about 1395":"oko 1395.","1416":"1416.","Scotland":"Scotland","Stornoway Castle, Lewis, Scotland":"Stornoway, Ross-shire, Scotland","Ross-shire, Scotland":"Ross-shire, Scotland","Lochbroom, Ross-shire, Scotland":"Lochbroom, Ross-shire, Scotland","Kintail, Ross-shire, Scotland":"Kintail, Ross-shire, Scotland"},"cs":{"1374–1416":"1374–1416","1370–Male":"1370–Zesnulý","1363–1416":"1363–1416","1398–1488":"1398–1488","1296–1380":"1296–1380","1325–1402":"1325–1402","before 1368":"před 1368","5 September 1402":"5. září 1402","1374":"1374","1363":"1363","1296":"1296","1370":"1370","1380":"1380","1402":"1402","1325":"1325","1488":"1488","1398":"1398","ab